                        <p class="mb-6 text-lg italic leading-relaxed text-[#e0e0ff]/84">"The pioneering work on Microtubule stimulation at Ultra Skool has given me my father back. After implementing the protocols, his cognitive function and memory have shown remarkable improvement. The intersection of quantum biology and consciousness is truly groundbreaking."</p>
